    <title>备忘录</title>
    <link href="/2022/01/19/%E5%A4%87%E5%BF%98%E5%BD%95/"/>
    <url>/2022/01/19/%E5%A4%87%E5%BF%98%E5%BD%95/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>hexo常用指令：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs hexo">hexo new yourBlog 生成文档yourBlog<br>hexo generate生成<br>hexo deploy部署<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>git 常用指令：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs git">git config --global user.name &quot;yourname&quot;设置用户名<br>git config --global user.email &quot;youremail&quot;设置邮箱<br>git config user.name检查用户名<br>git config user.email检查邮箱<br><br>git clone https://github.com/username/reponame.git 克隆下载仓库<br>git init初始化仓库<br>git status 查看工作区代码相对于暂存区的差别<br>git add . 将当前目录下修改的所有代码从工作区添加到暂存区 . 代表当前目录<br>git add &lt;filename&gt;暂存filename<br>git commit -m ‘注释’    将缓存区内容添加到本地仓库<br>git pull origin master先将远程仓库master中的信息同步到本地仓库master中<br>git push origin master 将本地版本库推送到远程服务器，<br>origin是远程主机，master表示是远程服务器上的master分支和本地分支重名的简写，分支名是可以修改的<br>git log 打印git仓库提交日志<br>git branch查看git仓库的分支情况<br>git branch a创建a分支<br>git checkout a切换到a分支<br>git checkout -branch c创建c分支同时切换到c分支<br>git merge a将a分支合并到当前分支<br>git branch -d a 删除a分支，参数为-D为强制删除<br>git tag为当前分支添加标签<br><br><br>Tip: <br>git add 是将修改的代码加入到暂存区中<br>git commit 是将暂存区的内容添加到本地仓库中<br>git push 是将本地的版本推送到远程服务器中<br><br>参考：Git的add、commit、push的详细介绍：https://www.cnblogs.com/nmydt/p/14256308.html<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>linux常用指令：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs linux">cdchange directory改变目录<br>mkdirmake directory创建文件夹<br>rmdirremove directory删除文件夹<br>touch创建文件<br>catcatenate连接 定向输出<br>vi用vi编辑器打开<br>mvmove移动文件或文件夹<br>rmremove删除文件或文件夹<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>windows常用快捷键：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs windows">win+d回到桌面<br>win+r打开运行<br>win+e打开文件资源管理器<br>win+tab 历史活动记录<br>alt+tab 切换窗口<br>win+space快捷切换输入法<br><br>shift+左键 全选两次点击之间的所有文件<br>alt+左键  独立选择文件<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>博客框架：hexo+github</p><p>hexo文档：<a href="https://hexo.io/docs/">https://hexo.io/docs/</a></p><p>CSDN的博客搭建参考教程：<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/sinat_37781304/article/details/82729029">https://blog.csdn.net/sinat_37781304/article/details/82729029</a></p><p>主题：fluid</p><p>官网：<a href="https://hexo.fluid-dev.com/">https://hexo.fluid-dev.com/</a></p><p>fluid配置指南：<a href="https://hexo.fluid-dev.com/docs/guide/">https://hexo.fluid-dev.com/docs/guide/</a></p><p>图床：picgo+gitee</p><p>picgo Github项目：<a href="https://github.com/Molunerfinn/PicGo">https://github.com/Molunerfinn/PicGo</a></p><p>picgo文档：<a href="https://picgo.github.io/PicGo-Doc/">https://picgo.github.io/PicGo-Doc/</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
    
